'''Open Whisper Systems'''（簡稱'''OWS'''）是一個[[非營利|非營利]]軟件開發團體，由{{le|莫克西·馬林斯佩克|Moxie Marlinspike}}在2013年創辦。他們主要專注在研發[[Signal協議|Signal通信協議]]<ref>{{cite AV media |people=Perrin, Trevor |date=2015-06-09 |title=TextSecure Protocol: Present and Future |medium=Video |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7WnwSovjYMs |format= |time=0:21 |location= |publisher=NorthSec |id= |isbn= |oclc= |quote= |ref= |accessdate=2016-09-24 |archive-date=2019-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190217115020/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7WnwSovjYMs |dead-url=no }}</ref>及維護相關的加密即時通訊軟件[[Signal_(軟件)|Signal]]。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tung|first1=Liam|title=Snowden's preferred messaging app Signal comes to the desktop with Chrome|url=http://www.zdnet.com/article/snowdens-preferred-messaging-app-signal-comes-to-chrome/|website=ZDNet|publisher=CBS Interactive|accessdate=2016-04-09|date=2016-04-08|archive-date=2017-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110223935/http://www.zdnet.com/article/snowdens-preferred-messaging-app-signal-comes-to-chrome/|dead-url=no}}</ref>OWS團體依靠捐款及資助營運，其產品皆為[[自由軟件|自由軟件]]。

